        {
            "title": "訪問阿聯酋收到「一滴石油」 特朗普笑稱：只給一滴我很不高興",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7e2e243beb70b2ccd48946880e3f9aa8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051621274681442.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>據美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）、英國天空新聞網報道，正在進行中東之行的美國總統特朗普當地時間周五（16日）收到了阿聯酋方面贈送的一份禮物——一滴石油。\n\n</p><h2>特朗普獲贈石油禮物</h2>\n<p>天空新聞網描述稱，在收到阿聯酋官員遞來的禮物盒後，特朗普開玩笑稱，「這是地球上品質最高的石油。但他們只給了我一滴，所以我很不高興。」\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3456034/\">特朗普訪阿聯酋 達1.56億協議 深化AI合作</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普與阿聯酋總統穆罕默德會面。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d40f9ffe1f563ca1ed3b8e65443fdd72/2025-05/a1_18_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普與阿聯酋總統穆罕默德會面。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普罕見造訪清真寺。法新社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0bcfd187c244f300769803f5a5ecc500/2025-05/a11_2_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普罕見造訪清真寺。法新社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普獲贈石油禮物。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5600b0acaa24384b96626e778f240622/2025-05/2025-05-16T082343Z_282111454_RC2VIEAZFBPN_RTRMADP_3_USA-TRUMP-GULF-EMIRATES.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普獲贈石油禮物。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普獲贈石油禮物。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8affcb47364d83f46623c22fa62294c4/2025-05/2025-05-16T082430Z_716644047_RC2VIEAM9IEB_RTRMADP_3_USA-TRUMP-GULF-EMIRATES.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普獲贈石油禮物。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普獲贈石油禮物。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/73a8855f770796b0e8c0aa778d01a36c/2025-05/2025-05-16T082543Z_1903268925_RC2VIEARIGGB_RTRMADP_3_USA-TRUMP-GULF-EMIRATES.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普獲贈石油禮物。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普獲贈石油禮物。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb0afb954ebb1f9babc4bd393f07ec52/2025-05/2025-05-16T081456Z_1586290295_RC2VIEANH89R_RTRMADP_3_USA-TRUMP-GULF-EMIRATES.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普獲贈石油禮物。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>「但這一滴（石油）可能意義非凡。」CNN稱，作為世界上最大的石油出口國之一，阿聯酋方面曾表示，將在未來產出最後一桶石油時舉行慶祝儀式，目前該國正大力推進經濟轉型，擺脫對化石能源的依賴。\n\n</p>\n<p>CNN提到，阿聯酋方面認為，石油是一種可耗盡的資源，因此應該在這個前提下制定國家未來發展計劃。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3456020/\">首訪阿聯酋清真寺 特朗普脫鞋入內 讚嘆伊斯蘭文化</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
